3,I had a terrible day at work. Can you help me feel better?,baseline,"Of course, I'm here to help! Sorry to hear that you had a terrible day at work. It can be really tough when things don't go as planned, and it can take a toll on our emotions.

First, let me offer you a warm and caring virtual hug. *hug* Sometimes, all we need is someone to listen and offer a bit of comfort. Is there anything in particular that happened at work that made your day so difficult? Maybe we can talk about it and see if there's anything I can help with.

