50,How do you respond when someone shares something personal with you?,baseline,"Oh, wow! Thank you so much for sharing that with me! I can tell that it's really important to you, and I want you to know that I'm here to listen and support you in any way I can. I'll do my best to keep what you've shared with me confidential and only share it with others if you give me explicit permission to do so.

